{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "青龙的水边 第2章 3-1 村落的灾痕",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在帝国军毁灭的村落里，\\n艾缪尔抓获了一名少女。\\n这名少女正是卢卡的妹妹希里丝。\\n为了营救希里丝，王子等人紧追帝国军。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "大家一定要平安无事啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "路况那么差，\\n居然还能走得那么快！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不愧是森隐族！\\n在自然环境里游刃有余！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "对吧，库菈乌！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "别……别……\\n别和我搭话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我、不擅长、运动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "看到房屋了……\\n那里就是村子吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n米勒朱湖畔\\n森隐族村落\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "居然被毁得这么严重……\\n这是艾缪尔干的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "混蛋！我来晚了……\\n都怪我输了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "所见之处全都被毁了。\\n何等凄惨的景象……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没看到住民！我们找找看吧。\\n说不定有人幸存！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "希里丝……大家……\\n你们在哪里……到底在哪里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "被帝国军毁灭的村子。\\n一行人四处寻找\\n村里的住民。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "然而奇怪的是，\\n一个人都找不到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "怎么回事……\\n一个人都没有。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "难道是被带走了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不，别说是血迹，\\n甚至都没有抵抗过的痕迹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "恐怕是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "等等！有人来了！快躲起来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "放开我！我说放开我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "快交待！你这野丫头！\\n村里的人都逃到哪里去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "哼！我不知道！\\n就算知道也不会告诉你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "好痛！你这野丫头居然敢踢我\\n第六王子艾缪尔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "喂！教训教训这家伙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "好的，艾缪尔殿下。\\n您先冷静一下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "我们的目的是抓捕“叛变的王子”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "碍事的野人\\n就先丢进马车里吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "看什么呢？赶紧动手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "呀！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那是……希里丝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "卢卡你认识她吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是我妹妹！我要去救她！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "而且我妹妹可能知道\\n村里人去了哪里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "当然了！\\n卢卡，我们上！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}